Package de.tum.cit.ase.maze.objects

Class Obstacle

java.lang.Object
de.tum.cit.ase.maze.objects.Obstacle
public class Obstacle extends Object
This class creates static obstacles in the MazeRunnerGame. It includes functionalities for loading obstacle animations.
